{"tid":370297,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"黑客爆料 泰維斯華朗古積特涉服禁藥","createTime":"2017-08-23T02:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T01:28:47.000Z","uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d99fa6a4aeb113b577abc88ccdfd1275c5dc654","tid":370297,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯網絡黑客組織Fancy Bear最近爆料，指泰維斯、華朗、古積特及軒斯等世界知名球星，在2010世盃期間曾被驗出服用禁藥，但仍獲官方許可在大賽中亮相。<br />\n<br />\nFancy Bear早前入侵世界反禁藥組織（WADA）的數據庫，獲取得大量秘密文件，並在網上爆出多名運動員的醫療數據，包括網球球星拿度及長跑名將法拉。<br />\n<br />\n《BBC》報道，他們最近首次爆出足球界的醜聞，列出25位在2010世盃涉用藥的球員名單，曾先後效力過曼聯的三位阿根廷國腳華朗、泰維斯及軒斯，以及上季掛靴、曾效利物浦的荷蘭前鋒古積特，都榜上有名，但這些球員均被WADA放入醫療用藥豁免紀錄（Therapeutic Use Exemptions）中，意味即使他們的藥物測試呈陽性，仍獲許可可在決賽周披甲。<br />\n<br />\n除四人外，德國中鋒馬里奧高美斯、意大利06世盃兩位冠軍成員伊亞昆達及甘莫蘭尼斯，同樣牽涉在內，當中以阿根廷多達五人，除上述三位前魔將，還有迪亞高米列圖及森美爾。"},{"pid":"f7f05024d49d901607b6df59eb714e4a2a335b78","tid":370297,"uid":83388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802d16f4e19efcd0a18c56fec03fefebee77837f","tid":370297,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2010<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07515c9bd059c602f3404600b1d6823c0972261","tid":370297,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4c2ec72d4dc2278773fa09171ad25cd286f776","tid":370297,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl